   "",
   "GENERATOR VALIDATION: VALIDATED (synthetic brackets real 2020 stylized facts) (3/3 regimes' synthetic moments match real-2020).",
   "",
   "Q(a) DOES COMPLEMENTARITY DD-DAMPENING HOLD/STRENGTHEN IN BEAR + CHOP?",
   "   bull     : mean blend-DD-vs-trend-alone = -0.3pp across cadences (neutral/worse)",
   "   bear     : mean blend-DD-vs-trend-alone = -11.3pp across cadences (neutral/worse)",
   "   chop     : mean blend-DD-vs-trend-alone = +1.3pp across cadences (DAMPENS)",
   "   stitched : mean blend-DD-vs-trend-alone = -5.6pp across cadences (neutral/worse)",
   "",
   "Q(b)/(c) DOES THE DYNAMIC ENGINE BEAT THE STATIC BLEND WHEN REGIMES VARY (stitched)?",
   "   GATE: sign-test p<0.05 AND paired-t p<0.05 AND mean net advantage >1pp (NOT a raw beat-frac)",
